title: Live: A Place To Rest [2001-2013] - Linkin Park (Live Compilatio
description: Hello all, I did a compilation of every Linkin Park song a while ago and uploaded it on here. I wasn't very satisfied, so now I redid the whole thing from scratch. I took more time with this one and picked out the performances that I liked best. This torrent uses both audience and soundboard recordings. I even mixed some stuff together as in Intros/Outros, etc.
